{"word":"ἀντέχω","slug":"ἀντέχω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀντέχω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀντί\">ἀντί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔχω\">ἔχω</a></el>] in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> only in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> ‘to have a close attachment to or interest in’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> <i>respect, esteem</i> <a href='B:470 6:24'>Mt 6:24</a>; <a href='B:490 16:13'>Lk 16:13</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> <i>extend help to, embrace</i></b><i></i> <b><a href='B:590 5:14'>1 Th 5:14</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp> <i>hold to, adhere to</i></b><i></i> <b><a href='B:630 1:9'>Tit 1:9</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀντεῖπον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀντί\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}